{"type": "article", "id": 24243, "title": "硫磺托盘", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-22T07:00:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607124455pMO5JYUxWZtfhACb.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这一系列的托盘来自冰岛设计师 Garðar Eyjólfsson，他使用了硫磺这种很少用在家具领域的材料。他通过数控将玄武岩磨出一些空缺，然后将熔融后的硫磺倒入其中，形成了黑色和黄色的镶嵌纹路，有点像肥皂盒。另外将 100 度到 120 度的硫磺倒入纸模具，等待结晶，就形成了一些小的硫磺块，与黑色的玄武岩一起是很古典的搭配。<a href=\"http://eyjolfsson.com/Sulphur-Archive\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124453KlcIY3e5UPrHhkXS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.17200855\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124453AEvgx2sQZTOV3iIj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124454YZh5TqoJx1BDFicC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65811966\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124454940EXP5B3xDveiYW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071244554n6sxWqVfULdu3l2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}